## Reference Internal Roblox Documentation

- Use the Atlassian MCP server to search for Roblox Confluence documentation, the Sourcegraph MCP server to search for Roblox repository code, and the Trino MCP server to query and learn about Roblox data stores. Make sure to use the relevant resource when you have questions regarding anything Roblox.

## Avoid Code Bloat:

- Make code as short as possible but do not stop working until the task is done.
- Only make requested changes.
- Do not write duplicate code - please look for existing solutions in the codebase.
- Avoid adding scripts to the codebase if possible. If you need to run a script please ask to execute it inline.

## Avoid Bias / Hallucinations:

- Consider alternative approaches before going forward with a solution.
- When debugging an error, please look for any error messages and proceed to write at least two paragraphs before proceeding to take action.
